'''伊森·傑西·柯恩'''（英语：Ethan Jesse Coen，{{bd|1957年|9月21日}}）是美國電影導演、編劇及製片。由於其作品的編劇、製片及導演都是親生兩兄弟共同合作完成，故被稱為「'''柯恩兄弟'''」。在個人事業上與{{tsl|en|Atlantic Theater Company|大西洋劇場}}製作舞台劇，並在《{{tsl|en|Relatively Speaking (2011 play)|Relatively Speaking}}》三部戲中邀來[[伍迪·艾伦|伍迪·艾伦]]和{{tsl|en|Elaine May|伊萊恩·梅}}共同編劇製作。

== 生平 ==
=== 成長背景 ===
伊森·柯恩是猶太人<ref name=Haaretz>[http://www.haaretz.com/culture/coen-brothers-boycotting-israel-is-a-mistake-1.361926 "Coen Brothers: Boycotting Israel is a mistake"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.haaretz.com/culture/coen-brothers-boycotting-israel-is-a-mistake-1.361926 |date=20160319194841 }}, ''Haaretz'', May 15, 2011</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.workingtitlefilms.com/features/qanda/id/7/q-a-with-joel-and-ethan-coen|title=Q&A with Joel and Ethan Coen|work=Working Title Films|date=November 16, 2009|accessdate=April 27, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180428013447/https://www.workingtitlefilms.com/features/qanda/id/7/q-a-with-joel-and-ethan-coen|archive-date=2018-04-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，出生在美國明尼蘇達州的[[猶太人|猶太人]]家庭<ref>{{cite web|first=Brian|last=Papish|url=https://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/03/16/coen-brothers-biography/|title=Everything You Need to Know About the Coen Brothers’ Cinematic Style|work=Highsnobiety|date=March 31, 2016|accessdate=April 27, 2018}}</ref>。他參加了美國威斯康星州的猶太人夏令營Herzl Camp（學習並慶祝[[猶太教|猶太教]]生活的營地）<ref>{{cite web|first=Gabe|last=Friedman|url=https://www.jta.org/2016/02/28/life-religion/9-famous-jews-who-attended-a-jewish-summer-camp|title=9 famous Jews who attended Jewish summer camp|work=JTA - Jewish news|date=February 28, 2016|accessdate=April 27, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180426075717/https://www.jta.org/2016/02/28/life-religion/9-famous-jews-who-attended-a-jewish-summer-camp|archive-date=2018-04-26|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。他於[[明尼蘇達州|明尼蘇達州]][[明尼阿波利斯|明尼阿波利斯]]郊區{{tsl|en|St. Louis Park, Minnesota|聖路易斯公園}}成長<ref name="twoheads">{{cite news |url = http://afp.google.com/article/ALeqM5gscDeHQbyybPqIAvt4N36wVwbkNw |title = Coen brothers prove two heads are better than one |accessdate = October 5, 2008 |date = February 24, 2008 |agency = Agence France-Presse |archive-date = 2008-03-03 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080303121431/http://afp.google.com/article/ALeqM5gscDeHQbyybPqIAvt4N36wVwbkNw |dead-url = no }}</ref>。母親瑞納（娘家姓為諾依曼）是{{tsl|en|St. Cloud State University|聖克勞德州立大學}}[[藝術史|藝術史]]學家，而父親愛德華·科恩是[[明尼蘇達大學|明尼蘇達大學]][[經濟學|經濟學]]家<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=PD&s_site=twincities&p_multi=SP&p_theme=realcities&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EF6EC4AB2DCD543&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM |title=愛德華·科恩 |accessdate=2015-05-10 |archive-date=2020-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200310051505/http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=PD&s_site=twincities&p_multi=SP&p_theme=realcities&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EF6EC4AB2DCD543&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM |dead-url=no }}</ref>。伊森·柯恩的母親是虔守傳統的猶太人，在對孩子的教育上她推動猶太教的宗教教育<ref>{{cite web|first=Sam|last=Adams|url=https://film.avclub.com/joel-and-ethan-coen-1798217972|title=Joel and Ethan Coen|work=[[影音俱樂部|影音俱樂部]]|date=October 14, 2009|accessdate=April 27, 2018|archive-date=2020-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201225022807/https://film.avclub.com/joel-and-ethan-coen-1798217972|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

於1976年畢業於{{tsl|en|Saint Louis Park High School|聖路易公園高中}}，並畢業於[[馬薩諸塞州|馬薩諸塞州]][[巴德學院|巴德學院]]{{tsl|en|Bard College at Simon's Rock|西蒙岩石分校}}<ref name="twoheads" />。接著進入[[普林斯頓大學|普林斯頓大學]]學習，於1979年獲得學位<ref name="twoheads" />。他的畢業論文是41頁的文章《[[維特根斯坦|維特根斯坦]]後期[[哲學|哲學]]思想的兩種觀點》。

=== 個人生活 ===
伊森的妻子是電影剪輯師{{tsl|en|Tricia Cooke|翠西婭‧庫克}}，他們有兩個孩子：女兒Dusty和兒子Buster Jacob<ref>{{cite news| url=http://articles.latimes.com/2004/mar/28/entertainment/ca-verini28| title=The United States of Coen| last=Verini| first=James| date=March 28, 2004| work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]| accessdate=March 15, 2012| archive-date=2012-07-15| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120715022534/http://articles.latimes.com/2004/mar/28/entertainment/ca-verini28| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.imdb.com/name/nm2955618/| title=Buster Jacob Coen on IMDB| accessdate=April 14, 2013| archive-date=2017-02-18| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170218124545/http://www.imdb.com/name/nm2955618/| dead-url=no}}</ref>。目前居住於紐約<ref>{{cite news |first = Ian |last = Nathan |title = The Complete Coens |work=[[Empire_(magazine)|Empire]] |date = January 2008|page=173 |accessdate =October 5, 2008 }}</ref>。

== 戲劇作品 ==
2008年1月，伊森·柯恩撰寫的劇本《{{tsl|en|Almost an Evening}}》<ref>{{cite news |last=McGEE |first=CELIA |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/01/06/theater/06celi.html?_r=0 |title=A Coen Brother Scales Down to the Stage |work=The New York Times |date=January 6, 2008 |accessdate=2015-05-10 |archive-date=2018-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180110182155/http://www.nytimes.com/2008/01/06/theater/06celi.html?_r=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>於[[外百老匯|外百老匯]]{{tsl|en|Atlantic Theater Company|大西洋劇場}}首映。2008年3月至2008年6月1日在紐約市布利克街劇院進行商業放映，由大西洋劇場和Art Meets Commerce製作<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.atlantictheater.org/ | title=Atlantic Theater Company | publisher=Atlantic Theater Company | accessdate=February 28, 2011 | archive-date=2021-01-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126142805/https://atlantictheater.org/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://www.artmeetscommerce.net art meets commerce – web design, internet marketing, videos, theatricals, events<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{Wayback|url=http://www.artmeetscommerce.net/ |date=20210126054926 }}.</ref>。

2011年伊森·柯恩寫了獨幕喜劇《{{tsl|en|Relatively Speaking (2011 play)|Relatively Speaking}}》<ref>{{cite news |last=MAY |first=ELAINE |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/10/16/theater/elaine-may-interviews-ethan-coen-and-woody-allen.html |title=Allen, Coen and May: 3 Wits, One Show |work=The New York Times |date=2011-10-13 |accessdate=2015-05-10 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111214742/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/10/16/theater/elaine-may-interviews-ethan-coen-and-woody-allen.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>在布魯克斯·阿特金森劇院10月20日，2011年該劇結束在2012年1月29日，這一季總共演出153場<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://artsbeat.blogs.nytimes.com/2012/01/04/relatively-speaking-to-close-at-the-end-of-the-month/?ref=ethancoen |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-05-10 |archive-date=2015-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518102811/http://artsbeat.blogs.nytimes.com/2012/01/04/relatively-speaking-to-close-at-the-end-of-the-month/?ref=ethancoen |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2013年伊森·柯恩寫了《Women or Nothing》，於9月16日在琳達總值劇院首演作為大西洋劇團的2013年至2014年季演<ref>{{cite news |last=KOZINN |first=ALLAN |url=http://artsbeat.blogs.nytimes.com/2013/05/23/ethan-coen-play-to-open-atlantic-theater-company-season/ |title=Ethan Coen Play to Open Atlantic Theater Company Season |work=The New York Times |date=MAY 23, 2013 |accessdate=2015-05-10 |archive-date=2019-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191002081327/https://artsbeat.blogs.nytimes.com/2013/05/23/ethan-coen-play-to-open-atlantic-theater-company-season/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

